title: Bobby’s Big Update On Mexico Wedding Date + Sam Hunt Feels Undeserving Of The Fame That Comes With His Music + One Hit Wonders Draft
itunes:title: Bobby’s Big Update On Mexico Wedding Date + Sam Hunt Feels Undeserving Of The Fame That Comes With His Music + One Hit Wonders Draft
description:
Bobby gave a big update on his friend’s destination wedding. He was asked 5 months ago and still didn’t have a date until now. Sam Hunt stops by to talk about his new song and how he feels like a reluctant star. We also do our One Hit Wonders draft.
